---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="RECO Consumer Information | Dongho Lee Real Estate"
  description="How RECO consumer information, representation choices, and the first consultation process work before Ontario real estate services begin."
>
  <article class="legal-page consumer-info-page">
    <header>
      <p class="page-kicker">Ontario Consumer Information · 온타리오 부동산 소비자 안내</p>
      <h1>Before real estate services begin<br /><span class="bilingual-title-ko">부동산 서비스 시작 전에 알아두실 사항</span></h1>
      <p class="updated">Dongho Lee, Broker · HomeLife Frontier Realty Inc., Brokerage · RECO #4773237</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <section>
        <h2>A website inquiry is not representation</h2>
        <p>
          Reading this website, downloading a guide, registering at an open house, or submitting an inquiry
          does not create a client or representation relationship. The first response may confirm your needs,
          timing, and whether you are already represented; it is not transaction-specific advice.
        </p>
        <p class="ko-copy">웹사이트를 읽거나 자료를 내려받고, 오픈하우스에 등록하거나 문의 양식을 제출하는 것만으로 고객 또는 대리 관계가 성립하지 않습니다. 최초 연락에서는 일반적인 필요 사항과 예상 시점, 현재 다른 중개인의 대리를 받고 있는지를 확인하며, 이는 특정 거래에 대한 조언이 아닙니다.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>RECO Information Guide</h2>
        <p>
          Before real estate services or assistance are provided, I will give you the RECO Information Guide,
          explain its contents, and clarify your relationship with the brokerage. The guide covers the benefits
          of representation, brokerage and designated representation, multiple representation, remuneration,
          and the risks of proceeding without representation.
        </p>
        <p class="ko-copy">부동산 서비스나 도움을 제공하기 전에 RECO Information Guide를 전달하고 내용을 설명한 뒤, 고객과 브로커리지의 관계를 명확히 확인합니다. 이 가이드는 대리의 장점, Brokerage Representation과 Designated Representation, Multiple Representation, 보수 및 무대리 진행의 위험 등을 설명합니다.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.reco.on.ca/recoinformationguide" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open RECO's official information · RECO 공식 안내 보기</a>
        </p>
        <p class="ko-copy">Self-represented party는 해당 브로커리지의 고객이 아닙니다. 기존 고객이 참여하는 거래에서 법적으로 허용되는 제한적인 도움을 제공하기 전에는 관련 RECO Information and Disclosure to Self-Represented Party 양식도 전달하고 설명해야 합니다. 이러한 도움은 self-represented party를 위한 조언이나 대변이 아닙니다.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>If you choose to be self-represented</h2>
        <p>
          A self-represented party is not a client of the brokerage. Before any permitted assistance is provided
          in a transaction involving an existing client, the applicable RECO Information and Disclosure to
          Self-Represented Party form must also be provided and explained. Assistance is limited and is not
          advice or advocacy for the self-represented party.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>What happens after you contact me</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Your inquiry is acknowledged and your general goals, timing, and representation status are confirmed.</li>
          <li>The RECO Information Guide is shared and explained before services or assistance begin.</li>
          <li>You decide whether to seek representation or proceed as a self-represented party.</li>
          <li>Services, remuneration, HST, responsibilities, and any referral arrangement are documented in the applicable written agreement.</li>
        </ol>
        <ol class="ko-copy process-list-ko">
          <li>일반적인 목표와 예상 시점, 현재 대리 여부를 확인합니다.</li>
          <li>서비스나 도움을 시작하기 전에 RECO Information Guide를 전달하고 설명합니다.</li>
          <li>고객은 대리를 받을지, self-represented party로 진행할지 결정합니다.</li>
          <li>서비스 범위, 보수, HST, 책임 및 리퍼럴 조건은 해당 서면 계약에 명시합니다.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Registration and contact</h2>
        <p>
          Dongho Lee, Broker · RECO registration no. 4773237<br />
          HomeLife Frontier Realty Inc., Brokerage<br />
          7620 Yonge St #400, Thornhill, ON L4J 1V9<br />
          <a href="tel:14166258241">416-625-8241</a> · <a href="mailto:contact@donlee.realtor">contact@donlee.realtor</a>
        </p>
        <p><a class="button primary" href="/contact/?source=reco_consumer_information">Ask a general question · 일반 문의하기</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
